00:21:48.135 --> 00:21:51.297
If we miss the fastest line

00:21:51.992 --> 00:21:55.154
We still learn where fountains shine

00:21:55.848 --> 00:21:59.011
The courtyard opens wider

00:21:59.705 --> 00:22:02.868
Than it looked in the printed square

00:22:03.562 --> 00:22:06.725
A bike bell rings behind us

00:22:07.419 --> 00:22:10.582
And scatters the afternoon air

00:22:11.276 --> 00:22:14.438
You fold the map uneven

00:22:15.133 --> 00:22:18.295
I hold the edge from the wind

00:22:18.990 --> 00:22:22.152
The building numbers blur out

00:22:22.846 --> 00:22:26.009
Then settle themselves again

00:22:26.703 --> 00:22:29.866
Tilt the map till north sits level

00:22:30.560 --> 00:22:33.723
Fold the square, loosen the stress

00:22:34.417 --> 00:22:37.579
If the arrows trade their place

00:22:38.274 --> 00:22:41.436
I can read it on your face

00:22:42.131 --> 00:22:45.293
Past the fountain, past the green

00:22:45.987 --> 00:22:49.150
Past the benches we had not seen

00:22:49.844 --> 00:22:53.007
You tilt the campus
toward the courtyard

00:22:53.701 --> 00:22:56.864
I find the step I counted wrong

00:22:57.558 --> 00:23:00.721
The seminar hall is closer

00:23:01.415 --> 00:23:04.577
Than either of us had guessed

00:23:05.272 --> 00:23:08.434
Your thumb rests over the legend

00:23:09.128 --> 00:23:12.291
Mine keeps the crease compressed

00:23:12.985 --> 00:23:16.148
We arrive with our
notes still scattered

00:23:16.842 --> 00:23:20.005
And a laugh we try to spend

00:23:20.699 --> 00:23:23.862
The map stays folded sideways

00:23:24.556 --> 00:23:27.718
Like the afternoon can bend again

00:23:28.413 --> 00:23:31.575
Angle the map till numbers line

00:23:32.269 --> 00:23:35.432
Fold the square, loosen the stress

00:23:36.126 --> 00:23:39.289
If we miss the fastest line

00:23:39.983 --> 00:23:43.146
We still learn where fountains shine

00:24:00.840 --> 00:24:04.602
Your notebook opens beside my notes

00:24:05.428 --> 00:24:09.190
Two headings lean in careful rows

00:24:10.016 --> 00:24:13.778
You shade a box, then lift the lead

00:24:14.603 --> 00:24:18.365
Before the thought is oversaid

00:24:19.191 --> 00:24:22.953
The lecture drifts
through ceiling vents

00:24:23.779 --> 00:24:27.541
I copy less of every tense

00:24:28.367 --> 00:24:32.129
Your pencil pauses at the side

00:24:32.954 --> 00:24:36.716
Where blank space learns to hide

00:24:37.542 --> 00:24:41.304
Leave the edge unfilled

00:24:42.130 --> 00:24:45.892
Let the white space hold still

00:24:46.718 --> 00:24:50.480
Some thoughts arrive too early

00:24:51.306 --> 00:24:55.068
Some stay better until

00:24:55.893 --> 00:24:59.655
You underline the reading date

00:25:00.481 --> 00:25:04.243
Then tap the desk and hesitate

00:25:05.069 --> 00:25:08.831
I fold my sleeve above the ink

00:25:09.657 --> 00:25:13.419
And give the open place to think

00:25:14.244 --> 00:25:18.006
A corner curls from borrowed rain

00:25:18.832 --> 00:25:22.594
Your graph bends toward mine again

00:25:23.420 --> 00:25:27.182
We trade a look, then trade it back

00:25:28.008 --> 00:25:31.770
The margin keeps its open track

00:25:32.596 --> 00:25:36.358
Between two headings

00:25:37.183 --> 00:25:40.945
There is space

00:25:41.771 --> 00:25:45.533
Between two breaths

00:25:46.359 --> 00:25:50.121
A careful place

00:25:50.947 --> 00:25:54.709
You do not have to write it down

00:25:55.534 --> 00:25:59.296
I do not have to turn around

00:26:00.122 --> 00:26:03.884
The class can keep

00:26:04.710 --> 00:26:08.472
What we almost found

00:26:09.298 --> 00:26:13.060
Leave the edge unfilled

00:26:13.886 --> 00:26:17.648
Let the white space hold still

00:26:18.473 --> 00:26:22.235
Some thoughts arrive too early

00:26:23.061 --> 00:26:26.823
Some stay better until

00:26:27.649 --> 00:26:31.411
Notebook margin, left blank

00:26:32.237 --> 00:26:35.999
A pencil waits, unpressed

00:26:36.824 --> 00:26:40.586
The unsaid sits beside the work

00:26:41.412 --> 00:26:45.174
And asks no more of the rest

00:27:03.000 --> 00:27:07.400
Last row packs in a paper rush

00:27:09.498 --> 00:27:13.898
Chair legs scrape,
then the hallway hush

00:27:15.996 --> 00:27:20.396
By the board where
the stairwell starts

00:27:22.493 --> 00:27:26.893
You press one pin through
a loose green chart

00:27:28.991 --> 00:27:33.391
I read the edge while
you smooth it flat

00:27:35.489 --> 00:27:39.889
Study circle, date moved late

00:27:41.987 --> 00:27:46.387
Your backpack zipper
keeps a crooked beat

00:27:48.484 --> 00:27:52.884
My straight-walk habit
slips at your feet

00:27:54.982 --> 00:27:59.382
I had the main hall fixed in my head

00:28:01.480 --> 00:28:05.880
You choose the stairs
by the poster thread

00:28:07.978 --> 00:28:12.378
Two floors down, the crowd thins out

00:28:14.476 --> 00:28:18.876
I learn the stairwell you think about

00:28:20.973 --> 00:28:25.373
If the notice leans, I lean too

00:28:27.471 --> 00:28:31.871
Only keeping pace with you

00:28:33.969 --> 00:28:38.369
Past the board, the handrail shines

00:28:40.467 --> 00:28:44.867
An errand takes its time

00:28:46.964 --> 00:28:51.364
Someone laughs by the vending row

00:28:53.462 --> 00:28:57.862
Your sleeve catches the paper bow

00:28:59.960 --> 00:29:04.360
You tap the pin till the corner stays

00:29:06.458 --> 00:29:10.858
Then point your chin
toward the longer way

00:29:12.956 --> 00:29:17.356
The lab would be quicker west

00:29:19.453 --> 00:29:23.853
But the stairs miss most of the rest

00:29:25.951 --> 00:29:30.351
So I tuck my shortcut under my tongue

00:29:32.449 --> 00:29:36.849
And the extra minute runs

00:29:38.947 --> 00:29:43.347
If the notice leans, I lean too

00:29:45.444 --> 00:29:49.844
Only keeping pace with you

00:29:51.942 --> 00:29:56.342
Past the board, the handrail shines

00:29:58.440 --> 00:30:02.840
An errand takes its time

00:30:04.938 --> 00:30:09.338
Half a floor above the noise

00:30:11.436 --> 00:30:15.836
You stop before the final choice

00:30:17.933 --> 00:30:22.333
The posted sheet
keeps fluttering there

00:30:24.431 --> 00:30:28.831
A green square shaking
in the stairwell air

00:30:30.929 --> 00:30:35.329
If the notice leans, I lean too

00:30:37.427 --> 00:30:41.827
One more landing, window-blue

00:30:43.924 --> 00:30:48.324
Past the board, the handrail shines

00:30:50.422 --> 00:30:54.822
An errand takes its time

00:31:13.786 --> 00:31:16.889
Projector cord across the floor

00:31:17.570 --> 00:31:20.673
Black curve running
from desk to board

00:31:21.354 --> 00:31:24.457
People drift with
their notebooks high

00:31:25.138 --> 00:31:28.241
You catch the trip in
the corner of your eye

00:31:28.923 --> 00:31:32.026
You kneel by the cart,
then loop it back

00:31:32.707 --> 00:31:35.810
Behind the table, along the track

00:31:36.491 --> 00:31:39.594
A strip of tape pins the cord down

00:31:40.275 --> 00:31:43.378
And nobody asks why
the curve moved round

00:31:44.059 --> 00:31:47.162
I stack the printouts, miss my cue

00:31:47.843 --> 00:31:50.946
Watching the cart
settle because of you

00:31:51.627 --> 00:31:54.730
The screen hums on,
the first group starts

00:31:55.412 --> 00:31:58.515
You fix the space
without a word or nod

00:31:59.196 --> 00:32:02.299
You tape the black curve down

00:32:02.980 --> 00:32:06.083
Before the first group turns around

00:32:06.764 --> 00:32:09.867
The floor holds steady where we pass

00:32:10.548 --> 00:32:13.651
A plain repair beneath the class

00:32:14.332 --> 00:32:17.435
Chairs slide sideways, bags tuck in

00:32:18.116 --> 00:32:21.219
The laptop fan starts whispering

00:32:21.901 --> 00:32:25.004
You coil the slack by the metal leg

00:32:25.685 --> 00:32:28.788
Then nod to the group
at the table edge

00:32:29.469 --> 00:32:32.572
I pass the notes from row to row

00:32:33.253 --> 00:32:36.356
The title loads in a pale gray box

00:32:37.037 --> 00:32:40.140
You check the tape
with your sneaker toe

00:32:40.821 --> 00:32:43.924
Then fade back into
the classroom talk

00:32:44.605 --> 00:32:47.708
You tape the black curve down

00:32:48.390 --> 00:32:51.493
Before the first group turns around

00:32:52.174 --> 00:32:55.277
The floor holds steady where we pass

00:32:55.958 --> 00:32:59.061
A plain repair beneath the class

00:32:59.742 --> 00:33:02.845
Then the floor changes shape

00:33:03.526 --> 00:33:06.629
A taped-down curve, a steadier way

00:33:07.310 --> 00:33:10.413
The aisle keeps moving, side by side

00:33:11.094 --> 00:33:14.197
While the black cord
stays out of stride

00:33:14.879 --> 00:33:17.982
The slide clicks in,
the speaker breathes

00:33:18.663 --> 00:33:21.766
Your taped-down work
sits under the scene

00:33:22.447 --> 00:33:25.550
I almost say what I understand

00:33:26.231 --> 00:33:29.334
Then pass the next sheet as planned

00:33:30.015 --> 00:33:33.118
You tape the black curve down

00:33:33.799 --> 00:33:36.902
Before the first group turns around

00:33:37.583 --> 00:33:40.686
The floor holds steady where we pass

00:33:41.368 --> 00:33:44.471
A plain repair beneath the class

00:33:45.152 --> 00:33:48.255
The cord lies flat by the table leg

00:33:48.936 --> 00:33:52.039
And the class goes on because of it

00:34:09.720 --> 00:34:12.439
Last slide before dismissal

00:34:13.035 --> 00:34:15.754
Blue-gray screen at the front

00:34:16.351 --> 00:34:19.069
Bullet points lose their edges

00:34:19.666 --> 00:34:22.385
While the ceiling fans hum

00:34:22.982 --> 00:34:25.700
You copy only the heading

00:34:26.297 --> 00:34:29.016
Then leave the rest undone

00:34:29.612 --> 00:34:32.331
I circle half a sentence

00:34:32.928 --> 00:34:35.646
And forget the second one

00:34:36.243 --> 00:34:38.962
The lecturer says review the chart

00:34:39.558 --> 00:34:42.277
Your pencil rests,
mine misses the mark

00:34:42.874 --> 00:34:45.592
The class is packing into sound

00:34:46.189 --> 00:34:48.908
But the thought will not settle down

00:34:49.505 --> 00:34:52.223
The sentence started opening

00:34:52.820 --> 00:34:55.539
Right before the screen went dark

00:34:56.135 --> 00:34:58.854
If I turned before the cursor

00:34:59.451 --> 00:35:02.169
Would you read the other part

00:35:02.766 --> 00:35:05.485
The projector kept on humming

00:35:06.082 --> 00:35:08.800
As the final bullet blurred

00:35:09.397 --> 00:35:12.116
When the final slide begins to fade

00:35:12.712 --> 00:35:15.431
I keep the ending blurred

00:35:16.028 --> 00:35:18.746
Someone zips up a jacket

00:35:19.343 --> 00:35:22.062
Someone laughs by the aisle

00:35:22.658 --> 00:35:25.377
You line your notes by chapter

00:35:25.974 --> 00:35:28.692
Then look over for a while

00:35:29.289 --> 00:35:32.008
I ask about the reading

00:35:32.605 --> 00:35:35.323
You answer what we need

00:35:35.920 --> 00:35:38.639
But something in the spacing

00:35:39.235 --> 00:35:41.954
Says more than either sheet

00:35:42.551 --> 00:35:45.269
The cursor blinks, the cables hum

00:35:45.866 --> 00:35:48.585
The last few minutes come undone

00:35:49.182 --> 00:35:51.900
I breathe as if the bell might know

00:35:52.497 --> 00:35:55.216
Which line to keep and which to slow

00:35:55.812 --> 00:35:58.531
The sentence started opening

00:35:59.128 --> 00:36:01.846
Right before the screen went dark

00:36:02.443 --> 00:36:05.162
If I turned before the cursor

00:36:05.758 --> 00:36:08.477
Would you read the other part

00:36:09.074 --> 00:36:11.792
The projector kept on humming

00:36:12.389 --> 00:36:15.108
As the final bullet blurred

00:36:15.705 --> 00:36:18.423
When the final slide begins to fade

00:36:19.020 --> 00:36:21.739
I keep the ending blurred

00:36:22.335 --> 00:36:25.054
All the chairs begin to turn

00:36:25.651 --> 00:36:28.369
All the practiced phrases thin

00:36:28.966 --> 00:36:31.685
You ask if I am heading east

00:36:32.282 --> 00:36:35.000
I say I have a minute free

00:36:35.597 --> 00:36:38.316
The screen goes dim across your face

00:36:38.912 --> 00:36:41.631
The class lets go of its last place

00:36:42.228 --> 00:36:44.946
I want to ask, but breathe instead

00:36:45.543 --> 00:36:48.262
And carry half the thought ahead

00:36:48.858 --> 00:36:51.577
The sentence started—

00:36:52.174 --> 00:36:54.892
Almost—

00:36:55.489 --> 00:36:58.208
The screen goes dark

00:36:58.805 --> 00:37:01.523
And the rest stays

00:37:18.088 --> 00:37:21.467
Window latch after class

00:37:22.209 --> 00:37:25.589
A silver click; the crosswind stills

00:37:26.331 --> 00:37:29.710
You check the frame and step aside

00:37:30.452 --> 00:37:33.832
Like ordinary work can stay

00:37:34.574 --> 00:37:37.953
The board is clean,
two blinds hang low

00:37:38.695 --> 00:37:42.075
Two bags lift from different rows

00:37:42.817 --> 00:37:46.196
I watch the silence gather up

00:37:46.938 --> 00:37:50.318
The part I almost told

00:37:51.060 --> 00:37:54.439
Keep it unhurried

00:37:55.181 --> 00:37:58.561
Hallway moving slow

00:37:59.303 --> 00:38:02.682
If we go lightly through

00:38:03.424 --> 00:38:06.804
I can learn that too

00:38:07.546 --> 00:38:10.925
You set the eraser straight

00:38:11.667 --> 00:38:15.047
I stack the copies by the wall

00:38:15.788 --> 00:38:19.168
The late sun stripes the floor

00:38:19.910 --> 00:38:23.290
But it does not feel gone at all

00:38:24.031 --> 00:38:27.411
Your zipper answers mine

00:38:28.153 --> 00:38:31.533
A simple sound across the aisle

00:38:32.274 --> 00:38:35.654
We do not seal the story here

00:38:36.396 --> 00:38:39.775
The last light rests awhile

00:38:40.517 --> 00:38:43.897
Keep it unhurried

00:38:44.639 --> 00:38:48.018
Hallway moving slow

00:38:48.760 --> 00:38:52.140
If we go lightly through

00:38:52.882 --> 00:38:56.261
I can learn that too

00:38:57.003 --> 00:39:00.383
Lower now, the campus hum

00:39:01.125 --> 00:39:04.504
Footsteps pass, then fewer come

00:39:05.246 --> 00:39:08.626
The latch is set,
the blinds are square

00:39:09.368 --> 00:39:12.747
Copies stacked beside my chair

00:39:13.489 --> 00:39:16.869
We close the frame and keep it there

00:39:17.611 --> 00:39:20.990
A daily task we both can share

00:39:21.732 --> 00:39:25.112
Keep it unhurried

00:39:25.854 --> 00:39:29.233
Hallway moving slow

00:39:29.975 --> 00:39:33.355
If we go—

00:39:34.097 --> 00:39:37.476
I can learn
